About this item

  • [ COMPATIBLE FOR M1 A2337/A2179/A1932 ] -- MacBook air laptop cover 2020/2019/2018case only compatible with the newest version of MacBook Air 13.3 inch laptop case 2020 2019 2018 new release with retina display and touch id (model code: M1 A2337/A2179/A1932), macbook air cover DO NOT compatible with old version (2010-2017 release) 13 inch MacBook air (model code: A1369/A1466).
  • [ CRYSTAL CLEAR HARDSHELL CASE ] -- Macbook air case Totally see-through crystal clear hardshell case, the macbook air 13 inch case cover laptop sign can be clearly seen, laptop back cover maximizes the original material of the MacBook and provides scratch protection for your 13" Mac Air. Snap-on design makes macbook cover easy to put on or take off.
  • [ ANTI-SCRATCH PROTECTION COVER ] -- Laptop hard case with all over protection for your laptop. Laptop protection cover made with high quality PC, macbook air m1 hard case with hard texture can well protect your laptop from scratches, crush, wear,etc. Macbook air cover 13 inch sturdy and durable to use.
  • [ EASY TO ASSEMBLE ] -- Waterproof laptop cover with 2-piece deisgn, laptop waterproof covers just snap in the protective cover along the edge of the screen. And the macbook air covers 13 inch perfectly matched vent slots in the bottom to keep your laptop stay good heat dissipation. The four caring rubberized feet if macbook air 13 inch cover can keep your device firmly in place.
  • [ HOW TO CHECK DEVICE MODEL NUMBER ] -- Please kindly check the model number "Axxxx" on the back of the laptop before your purchase cover for laptop, make sure you choose the exact same model number as the listing title stated "A2338" or "A2289" or "A2251" or "A2159" or "A1989" or "A1706" or "A1708".
